
## Examples
- First item: generate_key_between(None, None) -> "a0"
- After "a0": generate_key_between(Some("a0"), None) -> "a1" (or "a0z")
- Between "a0" and "a2": generate_key_between(Some("a0"), Some("a2")) -> "a1"

## Advantages
- No cascade updates when inserting items
- Items can be inserted anywhere without reordering
- Lexicographic sort matches display order

